============================================================================================
SECTION 9 — ESCAPING RULES
============================================================================================

JSON bodies — XML-escape:
  "  →  &quot;
  &  →  &amp;
  <  →  &lt;
  >  →  &gt;
  '  →  &apos;

XML bodies — same characters.

Regex patterns — XML-escape & in pattern strings:
  & → &amp;   (e.g., token=([^& ]+) → token=([^&amp; ]+))

Variable references — NEVER escape:
  ${SERVER}, ${PORT}, ${PROTOCOL}, ${Set_Cookie}, ${Location} — remain as-is.

